title: How to use OMI to play Mordhau Music from your piano (Not perfect at all)
description:
I did not do a tutorial about how to use my tool to play music in Mordhau.
So here is a demo of how you can do. That not perfect at all but that allows to test around.   
(Best solution is LuteMod and LuteBox but I don't have access to those.)  
Don't forget that there is a bard discord overthere (not mine):
